Lyrics :- 
Sath Pheron Se Bandha
Janmo Ka Ye Bandhan
Pyar Se Joda Hai Rabb Ne
Preet Ka Daman 
Hai Nayi Rasme, Nayi Kasame
Nayi Uljhan
Hont Hai Khamosh
Lekin Keh Rahi Dhakan

Tere naam ke harf ki tasbeeh ko, saanson
Ke gale ka haar kiya, duniya bhooli aur sirf
tujhe haan sirf tujhe hi pyar kiya

Tum jeet gaye hum hare, 
Tum jeet gaye hum hare, hum hare aur tum jeete
Mere dil ki dil se tauba, dil se tauba mere Dil ki
Dil ki tauba hai dil ab pyar dobara na hoga

Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol o yaara o yaara
Bol kaffara kya hoga

Humne dhadkan dhadkan karke,
dil tere dil se jod liya
Ankhon ne ankhen padh padh ke, 
tujhe vird bana ke yaad kiya

Tujhe pyaar kiya toh tu hi bata, hum ne kya koi jurm kiya
Or jurm kiya hai toh bhi bata, ye jurm ki jurm ki kya hai sazaa

Tumhe hum se badh kar duniya, duniya tumhe humse badhkar
Dil galti kar baitha hai,galti kar baitha hai dil
Haaye dil galti kar baitha tu bol kaffara kya hoga

Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol o yaara o yaara
Bol kaffara kya hoga

Dhadkan meri dhadkan
Dhadkan meri dhadkan
Dhadkan ………

snippet.title: Two Much With Kajol And Twinkle - Official Trailer | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Two Much With Kajol And Twinkle Official Trailer
Starring Kajol, Twinkle Khanna, Salman Khan, Aamir Khan, Govinda, Chunky Panday, Vicky Kaushal, Kriti Sanon, Varun Dhawan, Alia Bhatt, Janhvi Kapoor, Karan Johar.
Created by Banijay Asia

Official Release Date September 25, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Kajol and Twinkle are serving up a talk show with a twist - equal parts masti, magic and maybe even some manic energy. Expect wild hot takes, controversial opinions and the kind of honesty that makes you say, “Dude, same!” 
Joining them are their friends who just happen to be some of the biggest stars in the country (and even the world). With eight unique pairs gracing the couch this season, the conversations jump from filmy nostalgia to family drama, love, paparazzi, fame and everything in between.
What sets it apart is the unapologetic female gaze - a perspective that’s funny, sharp, and not afraid to hold up a mirror to society. One moment you’re laughing embarrassingly loudly, the next you’re caught off guard by an insight that might make you question your own life choices. 
Basically, it’s a vibe: two women side-by-side, yapping with their friends. Think of it as the fun table at the party, sunny, chatty, and just unhinged enough to keep you hooked.

Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,

ಗಂಡು: 
ಉಟ್ಟದಿ ನೀನು ತೆಳ್ಳನೆ ಲಂಗ ನೋಡಿರೆ ಸಾಕು ಬೆನ್ಹತ್ತಂಗ ಗಂಗಿ.. 
ಅದಿಯ ನೀನು ಪೂರಾ ಯಂಗ, 
ಯದಿಯ ಒಳಗ ಜುಮ್ಮ ಅನ್ನುವಂಗ 
ಗಂಗಿ ಯೆ ಗಂಗಿ 
ಹೆಣ್ಣು: 
ನನ್ನ ನೋಡಿ ನೋಡಿ ನೀನು.. ಮೈಯಾಕ ಮುರೀತಿ.. 
ಮುಚ್ಚಿಇಟ್ಟ ಆಸೇಎಲ್ಲಾಕಣ್ಣಾಗ ಸುರೀತಿ.. 
ಗಂಡಾ ಗುಂಡಿ ಅಗುನು ಬಾರೋಮಾವ ಒಂದು ಸರತಿ.. 
ಗಂಡು: 
ಗಂಗಿ ಗಂಗಿ ಗಂಗಿ 
ನೀಜಗ್ಗಬ್ಯಾಡ ಲುಂಗಿ.. 
ಚರಣ: 1 
ಹೆಣ್ಣು: 
ಗುಂಪಿನ್ಯಾಗ ಬಂದ ನನ್ನ ಸೊಂಟಾ ಯಾಕ್ ಹಿಂಡತಿ 
ಮೀಸಿ ತೀರವಕೊಂತ ಬಂದ ಯದಿ ಯದರ ನಿಲ್ಲತಿ 
ಗಂಡು: 
ಯಸ್ಟ ಬೆಳ್ಳಗ ಅದಾವ ಹುಡಗಿ ನಿನ್ನ ಕೈಯ ಕಾಲ 
ಒನ್ದ ಒಂದ ಕಪ್ಪ ಚುಕ್ಕಿಐತಿ ಸೊಂಟದ ಮ್ಯಾಲ.. 
ಹೆಣ್ಣು; 
ನೀಕಚ್ಚುಬಾರೋಗಲ್ಲಾ
ನಾ ವಲ್ಯಾಅನ್ನೂದಿಲ್ಲಾ.. 
ಗಂಡು: 
ಈ ಗುಂಡ ಗುಂಡನ ಗಲ್ಲಾ
ನಮ್ ಜಿಲ್ಲಾದಾಗ ಇಲ್ಲ 
ಹೆಣ್ಣು: 
ಮತ್ತ ತಡಾ ಯಾಕ ಮಾವ ಕೊಡಬಾರೋಬೆಲ್ಲಾ
ಗಂಡು: 

ಏ.. ಗಂಗಿ ಗಂಗಿ.. 
ಚರಣ: 2 
ಹೆಣ್ಣು: 
ನೀ ಉಡಾಳ ಇದ್ರೂಊರ ತುಂಬಾ ಹವಾ ಭಾಳ ಇಟ್ಟದಿ.. 
ಮಂದಿ ಇದ್ರೂಮೀಸಿ ಚುಚ್ಚುವಂಗ ಮುತ್ತ ಕೊಟ್ಟದಿ 
ಗಂಡು : 
ಊರಿಗ ಊರ ಐತಿ ಹುಡಗಿ ನನ್ನ ಮ್ಯಾನೇಜದಾಗ 
ನಿನಗ ಯಾರರ ಏನಾರ ಅಂದರ ಹೇಳ ಕಳಸತನ ಮ್ಯಾಗ 
ಹೆಣ್ಣು: 
ನೀಅದಿ ಬಲು ಘಾಟಿ.. 
ನಿನಗ ಯಾರು ಇಲ್ಲ ಸಾಟಿ 
ಗಂಡು : 
ನಾ ತಿಂದ ಬೆಳದನ ರೊಟ್ಟಿ
ನೀನೋಡ ಒಮ್ಮಿಮುಟ್ಟಿ
ಹೆಣ್ಣು: 
ಅಂದ ಚಂದ ಯಲ್ಲ ನಿಂದ ಮಾಡಿಕೊರೊಲೂಟಿ 
ಗಂಡು: 
ಏ.. ಗಂಗಿ ಗಂಗಿ.. 
…………………………………..

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. — This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Wednesday Season 3, the story continues in the aftermath of Season 2 as Wednesday finds herself entangled in an even darker web of family curses and rising threats. Hidden beneath Grandmama Hester’s watch, Aunt Ophelia resurfaces with a chilling prophecy that Wednesday must die, while Professor Capri and Tyler rally a growing army of Hydes to wage war against Nevermore. At the same time, Enid has vanished into the wilderness, lost to her werewolf form, forcing Wednesday on a relentless search that blurs the line between friend and foe. As ancestral secrets unravel and enemies close in, Wednesday must confront not only the cult determined to claim her bloodline but also the possibility that destiny itself has marked her for destruction. With higher stakes, fractured alliances, and a promise of unrelenting darkness, this new chapter teases a battle where survival may demand the ultimate sacrifice.
